  "detailed_description": "<strong>A challenging, silly, physics-based game.</strong> <br>Wibble is an adorable squid-like alien struggling with Earth's gravity.<br><br>Take control of Wibble's wobbly limbs. Maneuver through 30 increasingly difficult levels and face challenging obstacles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951680/extras/5b181e5767280ce0387cfa5260a97724.poster.avif?t=1654093615\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951680/extras/5b181e5767280ce0387cfa5260a97724.webm?t=1654093615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951680/extras/5b181e5767280ce0387cfa5260a97724.mp4?t=1654093615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Movement is relative to the direction the body is facing. Place yourself in Wibble's shoes - er, tentacle appendages - and Become one with Wibble!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951680/extras/a151a02f2a0fe193f9fbe2d1061dc0d7.poster.avif?t=1654093615\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951680/extras/a151a02f2a0fe193f9fbe2d1061dc0d7.webm?t=1654093615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951680/extras/a151a02f2a0fe193f9fbe2d1061dc0d7.mp4?t=1654093615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Steam Leaderboard</strong><br>  Compete against your friends and the world to get the best times! May the best Wibble win.<br><br></li><li><strong>Unlockables</strong><br>  Unlock skins and props by progressing through the game. Customize your Wibble!<br><br></li><li><strong>Challenging Levels</strong><br>  Journey through 30 unique levels with their own set of obstacles. Battle through guillotines, cannons, gravity and even cabbages.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951680/extras/6e421d84a24d3e22dcf7e1ec01180183.avif?t=1654093615\" width=400 height=162 /></span><br><br><br>Master the controls. Help Wibble get to the other side!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951680/extras/e56863ec877f375c01a525d9e785a3ac.poster.avif?t=1654093615\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951680/extras/e56863ec877f375c01a525d9e785a3ac.webm?t=1654093615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951680/extras/e56863ec877f375c01a525d9e785a3ac.mp4?t=1654093615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
